quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,Velleyli iza yaﾄ淒歛
  92,2,Vennehari iza tecella
  92,3,Ve ma halekazzekere velﾂｴﾃｼnsa
  92,4,ﾄｰnne saﾂｴyekﾃｼm leﾅ歹tta
  92,5,Feemma men aﾂｴta vetteka
  92,6,Ve saddeka bilhusna
  92,7,Fesenﾃｼyessirﾃｼhu lilyﾃｼsra
  92,8,Ve emma men bahﾄｱle vestaﾄ殤a
  92,9,Ve kezzebe bilhusna
  92,10,Fesenﾃｼyessirﾃｼhu lilﾂｴusra
  92,11,Ve ma yuﾄ殤iy ﾂｴanhﾃｼ malﾃｼhu iza teredda
  92,12,ﾄｰnne ﾂｴaleyna lelhﾃｼda
  92,13,Ve inne lena lelﾂｴahﾄｱrete velﾂｴula
  92,14,Feenzertﾃｼkﾃｼm naren telezza
  92,15,La yaslaha illelﾂｴeﾅ殘a
  92,16,Elleziy kezzebe ve tevella
  92,17,Ve seyﾃｼcennebﾃｼhelﾂｴetka
  92,18,Elleziy yﾃｼﾂｴtiy malehu yetezekka
  92,19,Ve ma liehadin ﾂｴﾄｱndehu min nﾄｱﾂｴmetin tﾃｼcza
  92,20,ﾄｰllebtiﾄ歛e vechi rabbihilﾂｴaﾂｴla
  92,21,Ve lesevfe yerda